# Sims Overlay

A browser-based animated overlay featuring Sims-style characters built with Three.js.

## Disclaimer
I do not own any of the models used in this project. All characters and their respective assets belong to their original creators.

## Model Credits
All Models are Ripped by Centrixe (previously Tiramisu6) @ The Models Resource.
https://www.models-resource.com/submitter/Centrixe/
-------------------------------------------------------------------
"You can shoot me a PM for whatever." -Centrixie
https://www.vg-resource.com/user-31358.html

## Built With
- [Three.js](https://threejs.org/)


#INSTRUCTION (IMPORTANT)!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
In order to use this with your OBS, you can either download all the files together, put them in a file together, and use the html file on the website overlay in OBS (there is a box for a local file under website)
ALTERNATIVE: This repo is live and can be accessed remotely by putting this "https://gord-d.github.io/SimsOBS/" in the website link of your OBS overlay!
